{"tid":1158272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向中環26歲女露體 警追緝四眼男","createTime":"2019-05-17T00:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T00:22:17.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"691965a626264f2213aa9f20680da246ed0fb62c","tid":1158272,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aws61ty.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAws61ty.png&h=3978f3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中區警方調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n中環皇后大道中一大廈，昨晚7時許，一名姓李26歲女子報警，指發現一男子懷疑猥褻露體。警員接報到場，搜索後未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n經初步調查，案件列猥褻露體，交由中區警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進，追緝一名男子，身高約1.65米，蓄短黑髮，案發時戴眼鏡、身穿藍色長袖上衣、米色長褲、白色運動鞋，及攜有一個深色斜揹袋。"},{"pid":"bba4b1b1e6f4f74ccd2afeb1141135161ed667f0","tid":1158272,"uid":144843,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:19:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe3b7fac665453a605c4ac6dd2fc84ddbc5d02a1","tid":1158272,"uid":60807,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T00:22:17.000Z","msg":"睇錯26歲女露體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}